com.yahoo.tensor.functions

Class ScalarFunctions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yahoo.tensor.functions.ScalarFunctions

  • @Beta
public class ScalarFunctions
extends Object
    Factory of scalar Java functions. The purpose of this is to embellish anonymous functions with a runtime type such that they can be inspected and will return a parseable toString.
    Author:
    bratseth
